  <text xml:lang="ta">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink95-kilavi">uṇṭik kālattu maṉaikkaṇ varutaluñ curuṅkip parattaiyiṭattaṉāyt talaimakaṉ
          oḻukiyavaḻi avaṟku vāyilāy vantārkkut talaimakaḷ colliyatu.
        </p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="Aink95">
          <l>karuṅkōṭ ṭerumai kayiṟu parintacaii</l>
          <l>neṭuṅkatir nelli ṉāṇmēya lārum</l>
          <l>puṉaṉmuṟ ṟūraṉ pakalum</l>
          <l>paṭarmali yarunōy ceytaṉa ṉemakkē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg xml:lang="en">

          <l> The man from the village surrounded by floods, </l>
          <l rend="indent4"> where the black-horned buffalo, after breaking and shaking off [its] rope,</l>
          <l rend="indent4"> gorges itself from grazing all day on long-eared paddy,</l>
          <l> has caused us agonising, unbearable pain every day. </l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
  </text>
